name: logzero
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "logzero" %}
{% set version = "1.7.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 7f73ddd3ae393457236f081ffebd044a3aa2e423a47ae6ddb5179ab90d0ad082

build:
  number: 4
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - colorama  # [win]

test:
  imports:
    - logzero

about:
  home: https://github.com/metachris/logzero
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Python logging made easy
  description: |
    Robust and effective logging for Python 2 and 3.
  doc_url: https://logzero.readthedocs.io/
  dev_url: https://github.com/metachris/logzero

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - carlodri
    - metachris
